{"tid":1460921,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係時候諗下點保住僅存非中資企業","createTime":"2019-08-13T05:24:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T11:28:56.000Z","uid":23499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9424650023abf0bbde1a99ae88af5be5fed05da4","tid":1460921,"uid":23499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:24:45.000Z","msg":"香港長時間被中資侵蝕<br />\n而家僅存嘅英資公司/香港公司好多已經比中資買入股份<br />\n但係唔緊要, 佢地一日未過半數一日都係屬於香港人<br />\n<br />\n望下滙豐國泰呢啲企業<br />\n已經睇得出中共係想乘機打壓<br />\n我地要諗辦法保住我地同行嘅企業<br />\n<br />\n佢地表面上點都要做野去順應中共要求<br />\n但係底子都係同緊香港人共存亡<br />\n<br />\n香港人, 加油!"},{"pid":"475f1f993c1a0a569f9f35d4dac9446fb9cdd8b3","tid":1460921,"uid":302419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T11:28:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}